Package: agentr
Type: Package
Title: Modular Agentic AI Framework in R
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver", 
           family = "Lee",
           email = "olee7149@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    agentr is a lightweight, modular R framework for building intelligent agents with identity, memory, 
    emotions, and LLM integration. Designed for automation, experimentation, and integration with other 
    packages such as 'okxr', 'binxr', 'strategyr', and 'tradesimr', it can be used for local companions, 
    Telegram-connected assistants, financial or news bots, and emotion-aware interaction systems. 
    Includes state management, emotional modeling, prompt composition, and data API integration.
